IPC::Open3::Simple
==================

IPC::Open3::Simple is a wrapper aroun IPC::Open3 providing
similar functionality with a somewhat simpler interface.

See perldoc for more information.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

IPC::Open3::Simple requires the following modules:

  IPC::Open3
  IO::Select
  IO::Handle

